| stats latest(value) as value by __well_num, metric_name | pivot __well_num metric_name value
| fillnull value=0 neftWellopAverageLiquidDebit
| fillnull value=50 neftWellopVolumeWater
| eval watercut=neftWellopVolumeWater/100
| eval density = 826*(1 - watercut)+1015*watercut
| fillnull value=density neftWellopLiquidDensityTm
| eval value=0
